nodes.text: The Feast of Prosperity chef battle was a cooking competition within the Feast of Prosperity to decide which of the two Hutts—Duuba or Gaboorga—should lead the organization of the event. The final decision was announced by the head judge, giving the victor control over the Feast of Prosperity.
The chef battle appears as the third part of the "Feast of Prosperity" storyline in the update 6.1.4 to the Onslaught expansion of Star Wars: The Old Republic.
